  "title": "Threat Intelligence with MSTICPy",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael and Sarah talk with guest Thomas Roccia&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/thomas-roccia/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/fr0gger_'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about threat intelligence and MSTICPy and more.\n\n                  <br>\n                  We also discuss Azure Security news about Azure Files SMB shares, Private Link support for Application Gateway, Managed Identities support for Capture in Event Hubs and more.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/996266?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/996266/\">MoreMSTICPy</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/996266/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/azure-files-rest-oauth/\">Public Preview: Azure AD Support for Azure Files SMB shares REST API</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/generally-available-application-gateway-private-link/\">Generally available: Private Link support for Application Gateway</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/generally-available-managed-identities-support-for-capture-in-event-hubs/\">Generally available: Managed Identities support for Capture in Event Hubs</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-infrastructure-blog/introducing-the-azure-linux-container-host-for-aks/ba-p/3824101\">Introducing the Azure Linux container host for AKS\n                     </a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://ndcconferences.com/\">NDC Conferences</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://github.com/fr0gger/unprotect\">UNPROTECT [PROJECT]: Unprotect Malware for the Mass</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://unprotect.it/\">The Unprotect Project: Search Evasion Techniques</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://store.securitybreak.io/threatintel\">Visual Threat Intelligence</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/security/blog/2022/06/01/using-python-to-unearth-a-goldmine-of-threat-intelligence-from-leaked-chat-logs/\">Using Python to unearth a goldmine of threat intelligence from leaked chat logs</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/msticpy\">MSTIC Jupyter and Python Security Tools</a></li>\n                     \n                  </ul>"
